dct_title_s: Chart of Rapa-Nui or Easter Island (South Pacific Ocean) to accompany the paper by J. L. Palmer, Esqre. R.N.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Locations of images [moai] and platforms [ahu] are shown. Settlements and routes across island are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 40, (1870), pp. 167-81; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.40 1870.
dct_publisher_sm: London: published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by J. Murray, Albemarle St., 1870.
